$eref.description: Structured values are strings—for example, addresses—that have certain constraints on their structure. Schema.org: http://schema.org/StructuredValue

description: The geographic coordinates of a place or event. Schema.org: http://schema.org/GeoCoordinates

___latitude.description: The latitude of a location. For example 37.42242.

___longitude.description: The longitude of a location. For example -122.08585.
